    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I disable my Instant Run by:</p>\n\n<p>Menu <em>Preference</em> → <em>Build</em> → <em>Instant Run \"Enable Instant Run to hot swap code\"</em></p>\n\n<p>I guess it is the Instant Run that makes the build slow and creates a large size pidXXX.hprof file which causes the AndroidStudio gc overhead limit exceeded.</p>\n\n<p>(My device SDK is 19.)</p>\n"
