    "question_id" : 25013638,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>For me non of the answers worked I saw here worked. I guessed that having the CPU work extremely hard makes the computer hot. After I closed programs that consume large amounts of CPU (like chrome) and cooling down my laptop the problem disappeared.</p>\n\n<p>For reference: I had the CPU on 96%-97% and Memory usage over 2,000,000K by a java.exe process (which was actually gradle related process).</p>\n"
