    "answer_id" : 55801343,
    "question_id" : 25013638,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I'm using <code>Android Studio 3.4</code> and <strong>the only thing that worked for me</strong> was to remove the following lines from my <code>build.gradle</code> file:</p>\n\n<pre><code>minifyEnabled true\nproguardFiles getDefaultProguardFile('proguard-android.txt'), 'proguard-rules.pro'\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Because <code>Android Studio 3.4</code> is using <code>R8</code> in <code>full mode</code> and is not direct compatible with <code>Proguard</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 9809771,
      "reputation" : 7300,
      "user_id" : 10699119,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/bXFpn.jpg?s=256",
