    "last_activity_date" : 1567726379,
    "creation_date" : 1567726379,
    "answer_id" : 57814067,
    "question_id" : 25013638,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>in my case, I Edit my  <code>gradle.properties</code> :</p>\n\n<p>note: if u enable the  <code>minifyEnabled true</code> :</p>\n\n<p>remove this line :</p>\n\n<pre><code>android.enableR8=true\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and add this lines in ur <code>build.gradle</code> , <code>android</code> block :</p>\n\n<pre><code>  dexOptions {\n        incremental = true\n        preDexLibraries = false\n        javaMaxHeapSize \"4g\" // 2g should be also OK\n    }\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>hope this help some one :)</p>\n"
