    "question_id" : 25013638,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Android Studio 3.5.3</p>\n\n<p>Find the Memory Settings (Cmd + Shift + A on Mac or click on Help and start typing \"Memory Settings\") under Preferences/ Settings and increase the IDE Heap Size and/ or the Daemon Heap Size to your satisfaction\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/h4rnA.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/h4rnA.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2150882,
      "reputation" : 531,
      "user_id" : 1907292,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/50baa624c3c285d563aa5c9144807c37?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "mburst",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1907292/mburst"
