    "last_activity_date" : 1577829699,
    "creation_date" : 1577829699,
    "answer_id" : 59548728,
    "question_id" : 25013638,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>At some point a duplicate copy of <code>apply plugin: 'com.android.application'</code> got added to my build gradle. Removing the duplicate copy and making sure all my apply plugins were at the  top fixed the issue for me.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
